or-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-pie5Fia6OX3GJydppNrLBw">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tứ đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第四段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Huy/T%E1%BB%AB-c%C3%B4ng/poem-99xZQ7Akm3pXsn53ts4RZQ">Từ công - 徐公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Huy/author-8x96YHLVSKlfkIiQP331OQ">Tạ Đình Huy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam-th%E1%BA%BF-ch%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-pwYVzZ3mpuX7PHg6BRMRqA">Việt Nam thế chí tự - 越南世志序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-huy%E1%BB%81n-ng%E1%BB%8Dc-th%E1%BB%91-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83m-trang-nghi%C3%AAm/poem-YNITS1r9wadWAqqDb-f5mQ">Vô đề (Lương huyền ngọc thố điểm trang nghiêm) - 無題（梁懸玉兔點莊嚴）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br></div>	</div>
